These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-1::.
House: craftsman, futuristic, gothic-revival
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, tulip, balloon-flower
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, yellow, blue
3 different pets are kept: turtle, rat, fish
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, swisher, bongani
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, november, october
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, taxi, airplane
 1. the owner of the fish is the person who likes blue##1
 2. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the craftsman house is the person who likes yellow##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 5. the person driving the trike is the owner of the rat##1
 6. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 7. the person who likes blue is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 8. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 9. the person who growstulip is the gothic-revival house##1
10. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |    3     |
| House      | craftsman  | futuristic   | gothic-revival      |
| Flower          | balloon-flower      | daisy     | tulip     |
| Color           | yellow | blue  | white   |
| Pet   | rat   | fish     | turtle  |
| Cigar   | old-henry      | swisher      | bongani      |
| Birthday   | october      | november    | july   |
| Transport         | trike    | taxi | airplane |

