.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk, juice
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, avocado, eggplant
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, lily, zinnia
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, havana, oliveros
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, rock, pop
House: futuristic, wooden, craftsman
3 different games are played: snooker, go, bridge
 1. the havana-smoker is in the middle##1
 2. the person drinking juice is the futuristic house##1
 3. the person playing go is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is the fan of pop##1
 5. the person eating pineapple is on the far left##1
 6. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 7. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 9. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
10. the person eating eggplant is the fan of blues##1
11. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage         | almond-milk | juice  | sprite     |
| Food           | pineapple        | avocado | eggplant    |
| Flower   | lily  | zinnia    | orchid    |
| Cigar   | oliveros    | havana    | bluemaster   |
| Music-Genre           | pop        | rock    | blues        |
| House         | wooden     | futuristic  | craftsman     |
| Game     | bridge         | go       | snooker |

