.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-17::.
House: cape-cod, gothic-revival, craftsman
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, monopoly, poker
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, bongani, pall-mall
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, sunflower, zinnia
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, february, may
City: new-york, edinburgh, colone
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, helicopter, jet-ski
 1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 2. the person who growssunflower is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 3. the craftsman house is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 4. the person driving the subway is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 6. the bongani-smoker is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 8. the person traveling to colone is in the middle##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
10. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
11. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |       3        |
| House      | craftsman   | cape-cod        | gothic-revival           |
| Game         | mah-jongg | poker          | monopoly      |
| Cigar           | prince   | bongani | pall-mall |
| Flower   | sunflower  | iris       | zinnia         |
| Birthday   | february    | may          | december        |
| City   | edinburgh  | colone        | new-york     |
| Transport         | subway   | jet-ski         | helicopter       |

