.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-18::.
3 different games are played: domino, backgammon, monopoly
City: rome, colone, paris
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, ambient, trance
3 different pets are kept: dog, fish, bird
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, grey, brown
House: ranch-style, colonial, futuristic
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, aconite, bellflower
 1. the person who growsaconite is the fan of ambient##1
 2. the colonial house is the fan of ambient##1
 3. the fan of ambient is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 4. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1
 5. the colonial house is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
 6. the fan of trance is the person playing domino##1
 7. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 8. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 9. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
10. the person playing backgammon is the person who likes brown##1
11. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
12. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |      3      |
| Game      | domino       | monopoly      | backgammon      |
| City          | colone        | paris | rome   |
| Music-Genre         | trance       | ambient    | d&b  |
| Pet           | bird | dog     | fish    |
| Color   | pink       | grey   | brown |
| House         | futuristic        | colonial   | ranch-style     |
| Flower     | bellflower          | aconite       | daffodil         |

