3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, tiparillo, fonseca
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, lawyer, analyst
City: edinburgh, miami, london
3 different games are played: whist, go, backgammon
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, drawing, puzzles
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, blue, black
 1. the person who likes coral is on the far right##1
 2. the person driving the train is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the lawyer##1
 4. the person playing whist is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
 5. the person who likes black is on the far left##1
 6. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far left##1
 7. the person playing backgammon is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 8. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 9. the person traveling to london is on the right of the dressmaker##1
10. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Transport      | bike      | train         | helicopter |
| Cigar          | tiparillo | fonseca        | ritmeester   |
| Job   | dressmaker | lawyer       | analyst   |
