The people use 3 different means of transport: van, snowmobile, subway
3 different games are played: go, billiard, canasta
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, mechanic, firefighter
House: townhouse, ranch-style, gothic-revival
 1. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
