 5. the person playing billiard is on the right of the firefighter##1
 6. the person who likes white is the journalist##1
 7. the ranch-style house is the journalist##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 9. the person playing canasta is in the middle##1
10. the gothic-revival house is in the middle##1
11. the person who likes purple is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
